Consider the following code that reads a file of student test scores and computes an average.

```java
Scanner scan = new Scanner(new File("scores.txt"));
int total = 0;
int count = 0;
while (scan.hasNextInt())
{
    int score = scan.nextInt();
    total += score;
    count++;
}
scan.close();
int avg = total / count;
```

